						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Espozo wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Maybe saving enough CPU time for higher sample rate music? <img src="./images/smilies/icon_neutral.gif" alt=":|" title="Neutral" /></div><br />The other points + economics. I've said before that coding in asm is about 10x slower vs coding in C. Having nicer sounds wouldn't make the game sell 10x as much.</div>

